{"tid":649843,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳平安好醫生(01833.HK)一手中籤率60%","createTime":"2018-05-02T00:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T02:55:28.000Z","uid":70951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a0e47306b244f2ca085767c7a0e8df361f8854","tid":649843,"uid":70951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T00:11:41.000Z","msg":"市場消息指，簡稱「平安好醫生」、由中國平安 (<a href=\"http://02318.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02318.HK&d=wi6JzRyH3hGS4W0KYr53tpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e0f36728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02318.HK</a>) 分拆的平安健康醫療科技(<a href=\"http://01833.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01833.HK&d=wi6JzRyH3hGS4W0KYr53tpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=36558d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01833.HK</a>)一手中籤率約60%，大約25,000人獲派一手，每50手穩獲一手。<br />\n<br />\n平安好醫生將於本週五掛牌上市，是次公開發售1.6億股，原本公開發售佔6.5%。早前市場消息表示，該股錄得近1,500億元孖展認購，超額約270倍。(vi/u)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=wi6JzRyH3hGS4W0KYr53tpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1137ee19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>\t<br />\n<br />\n一手好高中籤率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde30a7994ed062cc5f3697bf9018c70abae297b","tid":649843,"uid":138420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T00:13:11.000Z","msg":"平安心諗 正呀喂 你班傻仔幫我接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7b33f80a778718e089edf6f7c56692356b5208","tid":649843,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T00:17:11.000Z","msg":"平保跌到豬閪咁<br />\n有條撚概念咩 成班傻仔"},{"pid":"c0a3f388f9968282bca9679b52428c66270798c8","tid":649843,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.